Practice Programs

1. Print "Hello World".
2. Print your personal information.
3. Print multiple values using sep.
4. Print output using end.
5. Demonstrate all escape characters.
6. Create and print variables.
7. Perform all arithmetic operations.
8. Demonstrate assignment operators.
9. Compare two numbers.
10. Demonstrate logical operators.

